  Places to Find Elements

Here are a few of my favorite places to find external elements that I can use to composite assets into my scenes:

  • ActionVFX - A brilliant place to find beautiful action-related VFX elements from fire to smoke.
  • Shutterstock Elements - I helped launch this company a few years ago. Essentially, Shutterstock Elements features collections of various video assets that can be used to assist in the production process.
  • Envato Elements - A site featuring more affordable pricing for stock footage, elements, presets, and more.
  • Pexels - A collection of free video assets. Definitely worth checking out before you do a paid project.
  • Artgrid - Has some of the most cinematic elements you can find. The stock footage here is truly breathtaking.
